OL,3,CLos Angeles man wins $50 million
OL,4,Clawsuit over Starbucks hot tea spill
OL,6,FA Los Angeles jury has awarded $50
OL,7,Fmillion to a man who suffered
OL,8,F"catastrophic" burns after a cup of
OL,9,Fscalding hot tea spilt onto his lap at
OL,10,Fa Starbucks Drive-Thru.
OL,12,FThe incident happened in February
OL,13,F2020, when delivery driver Michael
OL,14,FGarcia used Starbucks' Drive-Thru
OL,15,Fservice.
OL,17,FThe barista handed him a tray full of
OL,18,Fdrinks, at least one overturned. CCTV
OL,19,Ffootage captures the moment the
OL,20,Fboiling tea spilt on Mr Garcia.
