OL,4,Clawsuit over Starbucks hot tea spill
OL,6,FHe had ordered three venti-sized
OL,7,F'medicine ball' hot teas, a wellness
OL,8,Fdrink which includes lemonade, honey
OL,9,Fand mint tea.
OL,11,FThe lawsuit said the barista
OL,12,F"negligently" failed to properly
OL,13,Fsecure one of the drinks into the to-
OL,14,Fgo carrier.
OL,16,FThe unsecured cup fell directly into
OL,17,FMr Garcia's lap within 1.4 seconds of
OL,18,Fhim taking possession of the tray,
OL,19,Fwith the lid popping off and hot tea
OL,20,Fleaving him with third-degree burns.
