OL,6,FNicholas Rowley added, "Michael
OL,7,FGarcia's life has been forever
OL,8,Fchanged."
OL,10,F"No amount of money can undo the
OL,11,Fpermanent catastrophic harm he has
OL,12,Fsuffered, but this jury verdict is a
OL,13,Fcritical step in holding Starbucks
OL,14,Faccountable for flagrant disregard for
OL,15,Fcustomer safety and failure to accept
OL,16,Fresponsibility."
OL,18,FIt took a jury in Los Angeles around
OL,19,F40 minutes to come to an agreement
OL,20,Fthat Mr Garcia should be awarded
OL,21,Fdamages.
