OL,6,FIn response to the verdict, Starbucks
OL,7,Fsaid: "We sympathise with Mr Garcia,
OL,8,Fbut we disagree with the jury's
OL,9,Fdecision that we were at fault for
OL,10,Fthis incident and believe the damages
OL,11,Fawarded to be excessive.
OL,13,F"We plan to appeal. We have always
OL,14,Fbeen committed to the highest safety
OL,15,Fstandards in our stores, including the
OL,16,Fhandling of hot drinks."
OL,18,FStarbucks had tried to settle with Mr
OL,19,FGarcia before the trial.
