OL,4,Clawsuit over Starbucks hot tea spill
OL,6,FThey first offered $3 million, later
OL,7,Fincreasing that amount to $30 million
OL,8,Fto settle.
OL,10,FMr Garcia agreed, but under the
OL,11,Fcondition that they apologise, change
OL,12,Ftheir policies and issue a memo to all
OL,13,Fstore locations to double-check their
OL,14,Fhot drinks before handing them to
OL,15,Fcustomers, attorneys said.
OL,17,FWhen they declined to agree to those
OL,18,Fterms, the jury eventually decided to
OL,19,Faward Mr Garcia with Friday's total.
